#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn8.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.12:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga "
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Vaṅgīsasutta "
msgstr "12. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.422, sc1
msgctxt "sn8.12:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā vaṅgīso sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Vaṅgīsa was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: hutvā → hoti (bj, s1-3, km)
#. VAR: vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī → vimuttisukhapaṭisaṃvedī (bj, pts2) | vimuttisukhapatisamvedī (pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.12:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā vaṅgīso aciraarahattappatto hutvā vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Now at that time Vaṅgīsa had recently attained perfection. While experiencing the bliss of freedom, on that occasion he recited these verses: "

# NOTE: This verse is consistently plural and it is not clear to me that it is not literally so, in reference to a group he hung with.
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn8.12:2.1"
msgid "“Kāveyyamattā vicarimha pubbe, "
msgstr "“We used to wander, drunk on poetry, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:2.2"
msgid "Gāmā gāmaṃ purā puraṃ; "
msgstr "village to village, town to town. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:2.3"
msgid "Athaddasāma sambuddhaṃ, "
msgstr "Then we saw the Buddha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:2.4"
msgid "Saddhā no upapajjatha. "
msgstr "and faith arose in us. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn8.12:3.1"
msgid "So me dhammamadesesi, "
msgstr "He taught me Dhamma: "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: khandhāyatanadhātuyo → khandhe āyatanāni dhātuyo (s1-3, km, mr) | khandhe āyatānāni dhātuyo ca (pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.12:3.2"
msgid "khandhāyatanadhātuyo; "
msgstr "the aggregates, sense fields, and elements. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:3.3"
msgid "Tassāhaṃ dhammaṃ sutvāna, "
msgstr "When I heard his teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:3.4"
msgid "pabbajiṃ anagāriyaṃ. "
msgstr "I went forth to homelessness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.423, sc4
msgctxt "sn8.12:4.1"
msgid "Bahunnaṃ vata atthāya, "
msgstr "It was truly for the benefit of many "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:4.2"
msgid "bodhiṃ ajjhagamā muni; "
msgstr "that the sage achieved awakening—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:4.3"
msgid "Bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnañca, "
msgstr "for the monks and for the nuns "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:4.4"
msgid "ye niyāmagataddasā. "
msgstr "who see that they’ve reached certainty. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn8.12:5.1"
msgid "Svāgataṃ vata me āsi, "
msgstr "It was so welcome for me "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:5.2"
msgid "mama buddhassa santike; "
msgstr "to be in the presence of the Buddha. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:5.3"
msgid "Tisso vijjā anuppattā, "
msgstr "I’ve attained the three knowledges, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:5.4"
msgid "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanaṃ. "
msgstr "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn8.12:6.1"
msgid "Pubbenivāsaṃ jānāmi, "
msgstr "I know my past lives, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:6.2"
msgid "Dibbacakkhuṃ visodhitaṃ; "
msgstr "my clairvoyance is purified, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:6.3"
msgid "Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, "
msgstr "I am master of three knowledges, attained in psychic power, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:6.4"
msgid "Cetopariyāyakovido”ti. "
msgstr "cxpert in comprehending the minds of others.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.1"
msgid "Nikkhantaṃ arati ceva, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.2"
msgid "pesalā atimaññanā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.3"
msgid "Ānandena subhāsitā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.4"
msgid "sāriputtapavāraṇā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.5"
msgid "Parosahassaṃ koṇḍañño, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.6"
msgid "moggallānena gaggarā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.7"
msgid "Vaṅgīsena dvādasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn8.12:7.8"
msgid "Vaṅgīsasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with Vaṅgīsa are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
